==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Maam
<hw>Ma'am</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Madam; my lady; -- a
colloquial contraction of <xex>madam</xex> often used in direct address,
and sometimes as an appellation.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> dame, madam, madame, lady, gentlewoman.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Maara shell</ent>⟦br⟧
